{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Accelerometer","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer\"><code>Accelerometer</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>构造函数</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer/Accelerometer\"><code>Accelerometer()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer/x\"><code>x</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer/y\"><code>y</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer/z\"><code>z</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Sensor\"><code>Sensor</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>Accelerometer</code></strong> interface of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Sensor_APIs\">Sensor APIs</a> provides on each reading the acceleration applied to the device along all three axes.</p>\n<p>To use this sensor, the user must grant permission to the <code>'accelerometer'</code>, device sensor through the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Permissions\"><code>Permissions</code></a> API.</p>\n<p>If a feature policy blocks the use of a feature, it is because your code is inconsistent with the policies set on your server. This is not something that would ever be shown to a user. See <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Feature-Policy\"><code>Feature-Policy</code></a> for implementation instructions.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructor","title":"Constructor","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"accelerometer.accelerometer_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer/Accelerometer\"><code>Accelerometer.Accelerometer()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Creates a new <code>Accelerometer</code> object.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"accelerometer.x_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer/x\"><code>Accelerometer.x</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns a double containing the acceleration of the device along the device's x axis.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"accelerometer.y_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer/y\"><code>Accelerometer.y</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns a double containing the acceleration of the device along the device's y axis.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"accelerometer.z_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer/z\"><code>Accelerometer.z</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns a double containing the acceleration of the device along the device's z axis.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Acceleration is typically read in the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Sensor/reading_event\"><code>Sensor.onreading</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> event callback. In the example below this occurs sixty times a second.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> accelerometer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Accelerometer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">frequency</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">60</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\naccelerometer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'reading'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Acceleration along the X-axis \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> accelerometer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Acceleration along the Y-axis \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> accelerometer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Acceleration along the Z-axis \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> accelerometer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>z<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\naccelerometer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">start</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/accelerometer/#accelerometer-interface","title":"Accelerometer"}],"query":"api.Accelerometer"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Accelerometer","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Constructor","id":"constructor"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The Accelerometer interface of the Sensor APIs provides on each reading the acceleration applied to the device along all three axes.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Accelerometer","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/accelerometer","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/accelerometer/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Accelerometer","title":"Accelerometer"}],"pageTitle":"Accelerometer - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}